item.title: Volvo Concept 26 Hints At Interior Design In A World Of Autonomous Cars

Volvo Concept 26 Hints At Interior Design In A World Of Autonomous Cars

A handful of firms has started showing off concept cars in which actually doing the driving is optional. Utilizing autonomous car technology, these concepts preview a world where cars are able to drive themselves, essentially becoming an office or lounge on wheels for their owners. Some recent...
